TO COMPILE THE FINITE-STATE TOKENIZER:

$HOME/irish/tok]$ make
(takes 5-6 mins)

Output: $HOME/irish/tok/tok-gael.fst

TO TEST:

a) $HOME/irish/tok]$ echo "an rud atáá rá" | tokenize -utf8 tok-gael.fst
or
b) $HOME/irish/tok]$ cat test.txt | tokenize -utf8 tok-gael.fst
or
c) $HOME/irish/tok]$ cat someothertextfile | tokenize -utf8 tok-gael.fst
